{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/GettingStarted","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator"]]},"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths are complex and LOVING creatures that require careful creation and a suitable habitat. After creating a sloth, you’re responsible for feeding them, providing fulfilling activities, and giving them opportunities to exercise, play and rest."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Every sloth has a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/name"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/color-swift.property","type":"reference"},{"text":". You can optionally provide a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/power-swift.property","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" if your sloth has special supernatural abilities."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"slothPower.png"}]},{"text":"Create a Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Create-a-Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To create a standard sloth without any special supernatural powers, you initialize a new instance of the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" structure, and supply a name and a color, as the following code shows:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["var sloth = Sloth(name: \"Super Sloth\", color: .blue, power: .none)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your sloth possesses one of the special powers of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"fire","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"wind"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"code":"lightning","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", you can specify this at creation:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["var superSloth = Sloth(name: \"Silly Sloth\", color: .green, power: .lightning)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you’re creating a large number of sloths, you can define your own random name generator that conforms to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/NameGenerator","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol, and use it to generate names:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let slothNamer = MyCustomSlothNamer()","var sloths: [Sloth] = []","","for _ in 0...100 {","    let name = slothNamer.generateName(seed: 0)","    var sloth = Sloth(name: name, color: .green, power: .ice)","    ","    sloths.append(sloth)","}"]},{"level":3,"text":"Provide a Habitat","anchor":"Provide-a-Habitat","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sloths thrive in comfortable habitats. To create a sloth-friendly habitat, you specify whether it’s humid, warm, or both. The following listing creates a habitat that’s humid and warm, which results in a high ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Habitat\/comfortLevel","isActive":true},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let lovelyHabitat = Habitat(isHumid: true, isWarm: true)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After you create a sloth habitat, you’re ready for sloths to sleep in it. Sleeping in a habitat increases the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/energyLevel","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" of the sloth by the comfort level of the habitat. Sloths sleep for long periods so, by default, your sloth sleeps for 12 hours, but you can also customize this value:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["superSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat)","hyperSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat, for: 2)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Exercise a Sloth","type":"heading","anchor":"Exercise-a-Sloth","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To keep your sloths happy and fulfilled, you can create activities for them to perform. Define your activities by conforming to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol and implementing the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct Sightseeing: Activity {","    func perform(with sloth: inout Sloth) -> Speed {","        sloth.energyLevel -= 10","        return .slow","    }","}"]},{"text":"Feed a Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Feed-a-Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths require sustenance to perform activities, so you can feed them "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/Food"},{"text":". Standard sloth food includes leaves and twigs:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["superSloth.eat(.largeLeaf)","hyperSloth.eat(.twig)"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Schedule Care for a Sloth","anchor":"Schedule-Care-for-a-Sloth","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To make it easy to care for your sloth, SlothCreator provides a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/CareSchedule","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" structure that lets you define activities or foods for your sloth to enjoy at specific times. Create the schedule, then provide a tuple of a "},{"code":"Date","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", or you can use some of the standard care procedures:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let events: [(Date, CareSchedule.Event)] = [","    (Date.now, .bedtime),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 12*60*60), .breakfast),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 13*60*60), .activity(Sightseeing()))","]","","let schedule = CareSchedule(events: events)","superSloth.schedule = schedule"]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"This is a test line . Create a sloth and assign personality traits and abilities to your Sloth. Have fun!!","type":"text"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/SlothySample","doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/slothcreator\/gettingstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"images":[{"type":"card","identifier":"gettingStarted-card.png"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"SlothCreator"}],"title":"Getting Started with Sloths"},"references":{"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator":{"type":"topic","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"slothCreator-icon.png"}],"url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator","title":"SlothCreator","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Catalog sloths you find in nature and create new adorable virtual sloths. Enjoy!"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"slothPower.png":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/slothPower@2